#0200
<DNP0199<KEY<FLJ0253:0201<MSGYou find a note written by
Booster.<NOD
Would you like to read it?<YNJ0000<CLR<TURBefore we came to the island,
there were already several...
'incidents'.<NOD<CLRSue's father, Daisuke Sakamoto,
was murdered in cold blood.
By whom, no one knows.<NOD<CLRThis was years ago, and it delayed
our trip here significantly.<NOD<CLRIt was originally Daisuke's idea
to come here. He said something
was 'waiting' for him here.<NOD<CLRI can only pray that this
'something' was not the crown.<NOD<CLRHowever, since Date seemed to take
Daisuke's death the hardest, he may
have been using the crown on his behalf.<NOD<CLRIn a dubious way, I'm glad things
turned out as they did.<NOD<CLRI would hate to think of what
would happen to Sue and Momorin if
Daisuke were to go mad like that...<NOD<CLRStill, I can't help but feel
sorry for Date after learning about
Ballos' influences on the island.<NOD<CLRWhat may have started as fulfilling
his partner's deluded dream turned
him into another mindless zealot.<NOD<CLRI hope, wherever they are, they
can rest peacefully.<NOD<END
#0201
<MSGYou find a note hastily
written by Booster.<NOD
Would you like to read it?<YNJ0000<CLR<TURI was a fool to have ever
doubted Daisuke, it seems.<NOD<CLRDate wants to see us all
killed. That was the entire
purpose of our coming here.<NOD<CLRHe's no longer human.
Is he in control, or is
it still Ballos?<NOD<CLREither way, I fear without
a miracle, the island's
time is nearing its end.<NOD<CLR
And us along with it...<NOD<END
#0500
