<SOU0043<ANP0500:0001:0000<WAI0010<MYB0002<WAI0001<MYB0002
<WAI0080<CNP0650:0113:0002<ANP0650:0030:0002<WAI0100
<ANP0650:0000:0002<ANP0500:0000:0000<WAI0050<MSG<FAC0024
Phew...<ANP0650:0000:0000<NOD<CLRI see you've made it
up here in one piece.<NOD
Good, good...<NOD<CLO<WAI0020<MSG
Hmmm...<NOD<CLRI don't know quite how
to tell you this, but...<NOD
There's been another
change in plans.<NOD<CLRMisery contacted us again,
just a few moments ago...<NOD
I don't know why, or how,
but...<NOD<CLRJenka's barrier has
fallen.<NOD And, moreover,
the island is no longer
in any danger!<NOD<CLR
Hahahah...<NOD<CLO<FAC0000<WAI0005
<ANP0650:0003:0000<WAI0039<MYD0000<WAI0007<ANP0650:0000:0002
<MSG<FAC0024I'm just as surprised as
you are!<NOD If what Misery
says is true...<NOD
Jenka should awaken
shortly, and things should
return to normal.<NOD<CLO<WAI0005<ANP0650:0005:0000<WAI0020
<MSGI'm sorry to have
placed so much pressure
on you, Quote.<NOD
I can't say I'd know
what to do if you
never came here.<NOD
But I suppose Jenka
knew you had what
it took, if she...<NOD<CLR
Hrm...<NOD<CLO<WAI0005<ANP0650:0000:0000<WAI0020<MSGStrange that you'd be
summoned here at all.<NOD
If her memory of Ballos
drove her to tear the
island apart...<NOD<CLR
Hmmm...<NOD<CLRPerhaps we'd do better
discussing this outside
while we wait.<NOD
Momorin and Itoh should
be here shortly.<NOD<CLO
